---
// Simple banner to direct visitors to the IOD job page
---

<div class="w-full bg-[#1e1e1e] text-white py-4 px-6">
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-4 max-w-7xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-semibold">Could you be our next Director of Infrastructure and Organisational Development?</h2>
        <a 
            href="/iod" 
            class="flex items-center gap-2 bg-white text-[#1e1e1e] px-6 py-2 rounded-lg font-medium hover:bg-gray-200 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap"
        >
            Learn more
            <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"></path>
            </svg>
        </a>
    </div>
</div>
